  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You and your allies pelt your enemies with a deadly barrage of missiles.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Point-Blank Shot, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When an ally who also has this feat makes a ranged attack and hits an opponent within 30 feet of you, you can spend an immediate action to make a single ranged attack against that opponent. Your ranged weapon must be in hand, loaded, and ready to be fired or thrown for you to make the ranged attack.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to make the attack granted by this feat as an attack of opportunity instead of an immediate action. You can use this combat trick only once per round.",
